title: **Welcome to 20r Gaming**
description:
Hello!

Welcome to the official 20r Gaming discord!

This is the place where your gaming experience travels **above and beyond!**

BUT FIRST.... You'll need to take some steps to get there!

First thing you'll need to do is place an application by copy/pasting the pinned format and answering the questions.

This can be found in <#763135307595644948>
 
While handing  in your application, you can go to <#744029774820933633> to join our public gaming channels and hang out with the people that plays the same games as you.

The last thing you'll need to do is wait for a recruiter to contact you, to schedule an interview.
